3
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:07,980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

4
00:01:08,020 --> 00:01:11,140
[Episode 7]

5
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:43,500
Xiuyuan?

6
00:01:44,750 --> 00:01:46,450
Xiuyuan? Xiuyuan!

7
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:51,340
Xiuyuan?

8
00:01:53,310 --> 00:01:54,010
Xiuyuan.

9
00:01:57,750 --> 00:01:58,340
Xiuyuan.

10
00:01:58,750 --> 00:01:59,450
Xiuyuan, wake up!

11
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:22,810
You need to wake up now.

12
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:25,130
We're not even yet.

13
00:02:35,710 --> 00:02:37,300
Xiuyuan, wake up!

14
00:02:37,990 --> 00:02:39,780
That scumbag Zong will come after us again.

15
00:02:39,990 --> 00:02:41,180
We need to get back to the academy.

16
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:43,300
Xiuyuan, wake up!

17
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:48,530
Stop!

18
00:02:53,670 --> 00:02:54,780
Are you that dark stone?

19
00:02:58,150 --> 00:02:58,810
I don't care what you are.

20
00:02:58,830 --> 00:02:59,620
Stay away from us.

21
00:03:00,430 --> 00:03:01,410
Wait...

22
00:03:01,830 --> 00:03:03,620
I can't carry you.

23
00:03:13,150 --> 00:03:13,850
For me?

24
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,620
Getting caught by Zong Quan means death anyway.

25
00:03:25,550 --> 00:03:26,220
Might as well try this.

26
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:46,650
Are you alright?

27
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:53,460
Xiuyuan?

28
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:55,410
What's going on with you?

29
00:03:55,670 --> 00:03:56,300
Xiuyuan?

30
00:04:18,470 --> 00:04:19,300
No way.

31
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:30,770
Xiuyuan!

32
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,210
Xiuyuan!

33
00:04:43,270 --> 00:04:43,690
Xiuyuan.

34
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:44,500
Let go.

35
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:45,180
I...

36
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,130
I'm Lifei.

37
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:51,810
Let go.

38
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:57,810
I'm Lifei.

39
00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:06,690
Let... let go.

40
00:05:16,230 --> 00:05:18,890
No. I can't die yet.

41
00:05:19,590 --> 00:05:23,370
Master, save me.

42
00:06:20,830 --> 00:06:22,060
Could it be the Divine Tree?

43
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:37,180
A disciple of Wuyue Court?

44
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:17,620
Xiaobangchui?

45
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:38,420
Lifei.

46
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:48,570
Lifei!

47
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,620
So fragrant.

48
00:07:58,880 --> 00:07:59,980
So fragrant.

49
00:08:43,230 --> 00:08:43,780
Lifei.

50
00:08:51,710 --> 00:08:52,300
Lifei!

51
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:57,660
Lei, how is she?

52
00:09:00,990 --> 00:09:01,660
Yue.

53
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:14,570
So you're all in this together!

54
00:10:01,590 --> 00:10:03,210
A disruption of the vital energy. Nothing serious.

55
00:10:06,630 --> 00:10:07,300
Mr. Zong,

56
00:10:08,350 --> 00:10:10,330
why do you keep harming my disciples?

57
00:10:10,750 --> 00:10:13,060
The Divine Tree's aura appeared in the forbidden area just now.

58
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:16,450
I suspect the Divine Tree is on them!

59
00:10:17,110 --> 00:10:19,060
I'm taking them back for inspection!

60
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:21,570
Mr. Zuo,

61
00:10:22,110 --> 00:10:23,690
Jiang and Lei

62
00:10:23,710 --> 00:10:24,780
were almost ambushed earlier.

63
00:10:25,110 --> 00:10:26,660
I came to the forbidden area out of concern.

64
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,810
I didn't see any Divine Tree aura.

65
00:10:29,750 --> 00:10:33,380
I only saw Mr. Zong trying to kill them.

66
00:10:33,590 --> 00:10:34,490
Nonsense!

67
00:10:35,110 --> 00:10:36,780
When did you collude with them?

68
00:10:37,230 --> 00:10:37,730
You old wretch,

69
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:39,610
if you want to wipe out Wu Guo's remnants,

70
00:10:40,110 --> 00:10:40,730
come at me.

71
00:10:41,710 --> 00:10:42,540
Leave others out of it!

72
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:46,260
I came to this academy on orders from my master,

73
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:47,180
Immortal Guangwei.

74
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:49,610
I never knew Lei before this.

75
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:51,690
Don't slander us.

76
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,490
You're intentionally protecting them.

77
00:10:55,990 --> 00:10:59,140
Is Wuyue Court trying to claim the Divine Tree for itself?

78
00:10:59,750 --> 00:11:00,140
You...

79
00:11:00,160 --> 00:11:01,260
The academy will investigate

80
00:11:01,710 --> 00:11:03,380
the Divine Tree matter

81
00:11:03,830 --> 00:11:05,020
and give everyone an answer.

82
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:08,330
Mr. Zong, you've harmed my disciples repeatedly.

83
00:11:08,800 --> 00:11:12,420
We can no longer keep you here!

84
00:11:20,990 --> 00:11:23,330
Jiaping, see Mr. Zong out.

85
00:11:57,040 --> 00:11:58,140
She's not hurt.

86
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:00,180
Why won't she wake up?

87
00:12:08,710 --> 00:12:09,850
After you fell,

88
00:12:10,230 --> 00:12:11,780
the Fragrance Bond started heating up.

89
00:12:12,040 --> 00:12:12,900
Mr. Mo said

90
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:15,060
you two were experiencing intense spirit power fluctuations.

91
00:12:16,280 --> 00:12:16,690
Xiuyuan,

92
00:12:17,510 --> 00:12:19,660
what happened in the forbidden area?

93
00:12:26,470 --> 00:12:27,140
So fragrant.

94
00:12:41,350 --> 00:12:42,210
Since it's a forbidden area,

95
00:12:43,160 --> 00:12:44,660
there are bound to be many bizarre things.

96
00:12:46,560 --> 00:12:47,660
Hard to notice.

97
00:12:55,230 --> 00:12:56,730
True. Glad you two are okay.

98
00:13:19,110 --> 00:13:19,780
Tongzhou.

99
00:13:22,990 --> 00:13:24,180
Do you smell a fragrance?

100
00:13:25,680 --> 00:13:26,260
A fragrance?

101
00:13:31,510 --> 00:13:33,060
What fragrance? No, I don't.

102
00:13:53,920 --> 00:13:54,610
Take care of her.

103
00:14:07,870 --> 00:14:09,810
This tea comes from far across the seas.

104
00:14:10,280 --> 00:14:11,380
Try it later.

105
00:14:15,630 --> 00:14:16,420
Back in the forbidden area,

106
00:14:17,280 --> 00:14:17,970
why did you help me?

107
00:14:23,800 --> 00:14:26,490
Does Wuyue Court have a grudge against Zong Quan?

108
00:14:27,320 --> 00:14:29,940
Wuyue Court is the number one immortal sect in the world.

109
00:14:30,800 --> 00:14:32,330
No matter how strong Zong Quan is,

110
00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:35,690
Wuyue Court has never taken Longming Sanctuary

111
00:14:35,710 --> 00:14:36,490
seriously.

112
00:14:40,710 --> 00:14:42,450
I told you before

113
00:14:43,630 --> 00:14:45,660
that I hoped you would join Wuyue Court someday.

114
00:14:47,350 --> 00:14:48,260
When that day comes,

115
00:14:50,040 --> 00:14:51,850
you'll be my junior brother.

116
00:14:52,750 --> 00:14:53,900
It's only natural for me

117
00:14:56,280 --> 00:14:58,060
to help my junior brother.

118
00:14:58,630 --> 00:14:59,210
Right?

119
00:15:02,040 --> 00:15:03,730
Go ahead and try it.

120
00:15:06,990 --> 00:15:08,060
Do you know

121
00:15:08,560 --> 00:15:09,570
what happened to me back then?

122
00:15:20,680 --> 00:15:22,420
Your constitution is already unique,

123
00:15:22,990 --> 00:15:24,900
and you were severely wounded by Zong Quan.

124
00:15:25,400 --> 00:15:26,260
You probably

125
00:15:29,710 --> 00:15:30,850
went berserk.

126
00:15:31,870 --> 00:15:33,300
Berserk?

127
00:15:36,470 --> 00:15:38,020
Does going berserk make you lose your mind?

128
00:15:39,110 --> 00:15:40,420
The spirits in the forbidden area are chaotic.

129
00:15:40,920 --> 00:15:41,940
Under their assault,

130
00:15:42,630 --> 00:15:44,210
your mind can get damaged.

131
00:15:46,230 --> 00:15:48,090
Just that?

132
00:15:48,750 --> 00:15:49,490
What else?

133
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:52,330
What did you think it was?

134
00:16:13,680 --> 00:16:15,420
When you go berserk,

135
00:16:16,350 --> 00:16:18,380
you feel a surge of powerful energy

136
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:20,420
that you can't control.

137
00:16:21,800 --> 00:16:22,330
But

138
00:16:23,920 --> 00:16:25,210
with proper guidance,

139
00:16:26,440 --> 00:16:27,810
you can make it work for you.

140
00:16:40,800 --> 00:16:41,690
There's a seal?

141
00:16:43,080 --> 00:16:44,940
Lei, are you okay?

142
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:11,900
My Lord,

143
00:17:14,270 --> 00:17:16,140
once you enters Wuyue Court, I...

144
00:17:18,310 --> 00:17:19,860
I will tell you everything.

145
00:18:21,550 --> 00:18:22,250
Where's Xiuyuan?

146
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:24,420
He went back to his room.

147
00:18:27,840 --> 00:18:29,340
Ye Ye and Gelin came by just now.

148
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:30,820
They got hurt too.

149
00:18:31,070 --> 00:18:32,420
But nothing serious.

150
00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:37,100
Lifei!

151
00:18:43,070 --> 00:18:44,690
What happened in the forbidden area?

152
00:18:45,840 --> 00:18:46,770
So strange.

153
00:18:54,160 --> 00:18:56,490
Lei, you need to rest and recover.

154
00:18:56,990 --> 00:18:58,530
Said you weren't going to Wuyue Court.

155
00:18:59,270 --> 00:19:00,580
And now you're already cozying up to her?

156
00:19:04,600 --> 00:19:05,340
Xiuyuan!

157
00:19:09,550 --> 00:19:11,290
Jiang, you're awake.

158
00:19:11,880 --> 00:19:12,940
How do you feel?

159
00:19:14,200 --> 00:19:14,860
Much better.

160
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:16,050
I came to check on Xiuyuan.

161
00:19:16,990 --> 00:19:17,820
Yue, morning.

162
00:19:18,840 --> 00:19:20,660
Lei's energy was unstable last night.

163
00:19:25,270 --> 00:19:26,620
He almost went berserk.

164
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:28,380
I was worried, so I spent the night

165
00:19:29,030 --> 00:19:30,140
regulating his breathing.

166
00:19:31,710 --> 00:19:32,620
All night?

167
00:19:35,600 --> 00:19:37,340
Lei was severely wounded by Zong Quan

168
00:19:37,360 --> 00:19:38,250
and hit by a nightmare spell.

169
00:19:38,880 --> 00:19:39,860
Given his condition last night,

170
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:41,660
without timely treatment, there could be dangers.

171
00:19:42,070 --> 00:19:43,050
That's why I...

172
00:19:45,990 --> 00:19:48,940
So it was a nightmare spell. No wonder he keeps strangling people.

173
00:19:51,840 --> 00:19:53,340
Thanks for helping Xiuyuan

174
00:19:53,360 --> 00:19:54,290
with his breathing.

175
00:19:55,440 --> 00:19:57,730
Jiang, no need to be so formal with me.

176
00:19:57,790 --> 00:20:00,050
We're both from immortal sects. We should look out for each other.

177
00:20:01,360 --> 00:20:02,180
Besides...

178
00:20:03,550 --> 00:20:06,100
Besides, if Lei joins Wuyue Court later,

179
00:20:06,920 --> 00:20:09,050
we'll be fellow disciples, right?

180
00:20:11,990 --> 00:20:14,340
You two carry on. I'm going back to my room to rest.

181
00:20:15,920 --> 00:20:17,010
- Wait! - Lei.

182
00:20:18,550 --> 00:20:19,050
Lifei!

183
00:20:19,990 --> 00:20:20,660
Lifei!

184
00:20:20,840 --> 00:20:25,420
Mr. Zuo Qiu is calling for you.

185
00:20:28,070 --> 00:20:30,690
Good-looking people

186
00:20:31,310 --> 00:20:32,290
are just popular.

187
00:20:34,360 --> 00:20:35,100
Now?

188
00:20:43,030 --> 00:20:44,620
Zong Quan was absolutely ferocious,

189
00:20:44,640 --> 00:20:45,900
chasing me all that way.

190
00:20:46,400 --> 00:20:47,530
If Xiuyuan hadn't stopped him,

191
00:20:47,960 --> 00:20:49,580
you wouldn't have seen me again.

192
00:20:53,470 --> 00:20:54,690
So it really was Zong Quan's doing.

193
00:20:55,200 --> 00:20:56,450
He almost hurt Yue too.

194
00:20:56,790 --> 00:20:58,490
Ms. Lin checked the chessboard formation.

195
00:20:58,880 --> 00:21:00,340
It was damaged by Longming Sanctuary's techniques.

196
00:21:01,440 --> 00:21:03,820
Elder Zong had been planning this all along.

197
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:06,900
We were too lax in our defenses

198
00:21:07,680 --> 00:21:10,180
and let our students suffer this.

199
00:21:13,270 --> 00:21:14,210
What happened next?

200
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:15,970
Next...

201
00:21:16,550 --> 00:21:18,290
That dark stone

202
00:21:18,400 --> 00:21:19,770
turned into a little figure

203
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:22,010
and gave me some kind of red fruit.

204
00:21:22,400 --> 00:21:23,420
I fed it to Xiuyuan.

205
00:21:23,880 --> 00:21:26,770
After that, I don't really remember.

206
00:21:27,790 --> 00:21:30,290
It seems it meant no harm.

207
00:21:30,840 --> 00:21:33,940
It even found you the Vermilion Fruit, a healing treasure

208
00:21:34,310 --> 00:21:35,100
from the forbidden area.

209
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:47,580
I found it where Lifei passed out.

210
00:21:47,960 --> 00:21:49,580
So it's not a Chaos Stone,

211
00:21:49,990 --> 00:21:51,050
but an island stone.

212
00:21:51,510 --> 00:21:54,010
Over time, it absorbed spirit energy

213
00:21:54,230 --> 00:21:55,770
and was able to awaken and take form.

214
00:21:56,990 --> 00:21:57,530
The Divine Tree!

215
00:22:00,230 --> 00:22:01,100
The Divine Tree's aura!

216
00:22:19,750 --> 00:22:20,380
The Divine Tree?

217
00:22:20,990 --> 00:22:22,770
Since you were able to awaken and take form,

218
00:22:23,310 --> 00:22:26,490
you must have gone through quite a journey.

219
00:22:26,840 --> 00:22:28,860
Why do you have the Divine Tree's aura on you?

220
00:22:29,550 --> 00:22:30,420
Can you tell us?

221
00:22:41,360 --> 00:22:42,380
This is...

222
00:22:44,840 --> 00:22:46,420
This is the Divine Tree Island!

223
00:22:47,710 --> 00:22:49,340
I've seen it in ancient texts!

224
00:23:01,640 --> 00:23:02,730
Is that strange dream of mine

225
00:23:03,440 --> 00:23:05,250
because of this stone?

226
00:23:15,790 --> 00:23:17,620
So it's an island stone from Divine Tree Island.

227
00:23:18,270 --> 00:23:19,140
Over time,

228
00:23:19,400 --> 00:23:20,730
it absorbed the Divine Tree's aura.

229
00:23:21,310 --> 00:23:22,620
That explains everything.

230
00:23:23,200 --> 00:23:24,100
After all that,

231
00:23:24,640 --> 00:23:25,900
it's just a stone.

232
00:23:26,680 --> 00:23:27,860
What a letdown.

233
00:23:29,310 --> 00:23:29,940
Elder Zhu,

234
00:23:30,270 --> 00:23:33,250
it's better that it doesn't reveal itself.

235
00:23:33,960 --> 00:23:36,970
Otherwise, it would invite greed and trouble.

236
00:23:43,470 --> 00:23:44,100
Everyone,

237
00:23:44,440 --> 00:23:46,180
the truth about the Divine Tree is now clear.

238
00:23:46,550 --> 00:23:48,180
We've been here for several days now.

239
00:23:48,750 --> 00:23:49,820
We won't disturb you further.

240
00:23:50,270 --> 00:23:51,210
We'll return to Wuyue Court

241
00:23:51,440 --> 00:23:52,490
to report to our master.

242
00:24:07,470 --> 00:24:08,380
Zhu Guangyan.

243
00:24:10,270 --> 00:24:11,140
Li Shengman

244
00:24:12,030 --> 00:24:13,050
Zhao Mingli.

245
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:14,820
Wang Zhiwei.

246
00:24:15,550 --> 00:24:16,660
Yin Ziduan.

247
00:24:18,600 --> 00:24:19,580
These seven

248
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:23,290
are the ones who failed the monthly exam.

249
00:24:26,920 --> 00:24:28,210
There are many paths in this world,

250
00:24:28,550 --> 00:24:29,860
not just cultivation.

251
00:24:30,360 --> 00:24:31,820
Hope you find your own path

252
00:24:32,360 --> 00:24:33,140
after leaving here.

253
00:24:37,310 --> 00:24:38,180
I've outsmarted myself.

254
00:24:39,070 --> 00:24:40,580
How am I supposed to leave here and save Shanhua?

255
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:46,490
Great!

256
00:24:48,640 --> 00:24:50,250
I knew our hard work paid off.

257
00:24:50,510 --> 00:24:51,050
Tongzhou,

258
00:24:51,230 --> 00:24:52,290
let's tell His Majesty

259
00:24:52,310 --> 00:24:52,940
the good news.

260
00:24:53,120 --> 00:24:53,820
He must be waiting.

261
00:24:55,310 --> 00:24:55,860
Let's go.

262
00:24:56,680 --> 00:24:57,900
Your Highness. Your Ladyship!

263
00:24:58,680 --> 00:24:59,100
Follow me.

264
00:25:05,550 --> 00:25:06,250
You guys go ahead.

265
00:25:15,030 --> 00:25:16,530
Good thing we passed the monthly exam.

266
00:25:16,750 --> 00:25:18,050
Didn't let Hu Jiaping win.

267
00:25:18,550 --> 00:25:20,290
Or our suffering in the forbidden area would've been for nothing.

268
00:25:20,440 --> 00:25:20,970
Right?

269
00:25:45,160 --> 00:25:46,010
I heard

270
00:25:46,440 --> 00:25:48,380
you're going to Wuyue Court with Yue?

271
00:25:52,270 --> 00:25:54,010
If you have Wuyue Court's protection,

272
00:25:54,550 --> 00:25:55,970
you won't have to fear Longming Sanctuary.

273
00:25:57,990 --> 00:25:58,660
I'm going to cultivate.

274
00:26:00,960 --> 00:26:01,450
You...

275
00:26:04,360 --> 00:26:05,420
You choked me under that nightmare spell

276
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:06,340
and I didn't hold it against you.

277
00:26:06,550 --> 00:26:07,730
Now you're avoiding me?

278
00:26:08,400 --> 00:26:10,100
Found a better backer, so you're turning on me?

279
00:26:14,990 --> 00:26:15,940
What is wrong with me?

280
00:26:17,360 --> 00:26:18,490
Why is it that whenever Lifei gets close,

281
00:26:19,510 --> 00:26:20,900
I feel like I want to...?

282
00:26:30,070 --> 00:26:30,860
What am I even thinking?

283
00:26:32,030 --> 00:26:33,140
Shanhua is waiting for me to save him.

284
00:26:42,880 --> 00:26:44,380
Tongzhou, what's wrong?

285
00:26:45,600 --> 00:26:46,210
Nothing.

286
00:26:48,920 --> 00:26:49,490
Your Highness,

287
00:26:50,510 --> 00:26:51,580
please save my brother.

288
00:26:52,470 --> 00:26:53,660
But this isn't the Yue State.

289
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:55,530
What can Tongzhou do?

290
00:26:55,990 --> 00:26:58,180
Your... Your Highness, save me. I don't want to die.

291
00:26:58,310 --> 00:26:59,860
I'll... I'll work hard on my cultivation.

292
00:27:05,640 --> 00:27:07,180
Take this to Xingzheng Hall

293
00:27:07,600 --> 00:27:08,580
and find Elder Xuanshanzi.

294
00:27:09,270 --> 00:27:10,420
He'll take you in.

295
00:27:13,200 --> 00:27:13,730
Thank you, Your Highness.

296
00:27:13,750 --> 00:27:14,450
Thank you, Your Highness.

297
00:27:22,960 --> 00:27:23,900
You're willing to help me?

298
00:27:27,710 --> 00:27:29,690
I want to know if Shanhua is safe

299
00:27:30,310 --> 00:27:32,290
and if Zhenyunzi is taking good care of him.

300
00:27:34,120 --> 00:27:34,820
I'm really worried about him.

301
00:27:36,550 --> 00:27:39,140
Don't worry. I'll handle this.

302
00:27:42,840 --> 00:27:44,970
I know something unusual happened between you and Lifei

303
00:27:44,990 --> 00:27:46,450
in the forbidden area.

304
00:27:47,270 --> 00:27:48,450
But if you don't want to talk about it,

305
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:49,530
I won't ask.

306
00:27:51,710 --> 00:27:52,660
I'm just glad you're safe.

307
00:27:56,600 --> 00:27:58,530
At the academy, you have people looking out for you.

308
00:27:59,200 --> 00:27:59,940
After we leave,

309
00:28:00,510 --> 00:28:02,010
we'll stick together just like we did

310
00:28:02,710 --> 00:28:04,450
in this monthly exam.

311
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:07,100
If I make it to that day,

312
00:28:08,270 --> 00:28:09,180
and if we're all still the same,

313
00:28:10,360 --> 00:28:11,210
then yes.

314
00:28:20,030 --> 00:28:20,420
Go away.

315
00:28:33,960 --> 00:28:36,180
Though Yue left without you,

316
00:28:36,470 --> 00:28:37,420
as long as you work hard,

317
00:28:37,440 --> 00:28:38,770
you can get into Wuyue Court.

318
00:28:43,640 --> 00:28:44,660
If you can't get into Wuyue Court,

319
00:28:45,030 --> 00:28:46,010
come to Xingzheng Hall.

320
00:28:49,750 --> 00:28:50,450
Oh, Lifei...

321
00:28:57,990 --> 00:28:59,290
Why are there so many bees and butterflies?

322
00:28:59,310 --> 00:28:59,900
Tongzhou,

323
00:29:00,270 --> 00:29:02,250
what kind of trick is she pulling to attract them?

324
00:29:04,710 --> 00:29:06,860
Lifei? Lifei,

325
00:29:07,440 --> 00:29:08,620
why are all these bees and butterflies

326
00:29:08,640 --> 00:29:09,940
circling you?

327
00:29:12,070 --> 00:29:14,210
The flowers in my room are too fragrant.

328
00:29:14,440 --> 00:29:15,420
I've been soaked in the scent.

329
00:29:20,360 --> 00:29:21,530
Zong Quan

330
00:29:21,550 --> 00:29:22,970
clearly isn't letting this go.

331
00:29:23,710 --> 00:29:25,530
We need to practice that Demon-Subduing Formation

332
00:29:25,960 --> 00:29:27,730
you mentioned. No slacking off.

333
00:29:30,510 --> 00:29:31,250
Gelin's right.

334
00:29:31,920 --> 00:29:33,620
Prepare for the worst.

335
00:29:38,440 --> 00:29:39,580
The formation only needs five people.

336
00:29:40,120 --> 00:29:41,900
But all six of us should learn it.

337
00:29:42,400 --> 00:29:43,340
If someone gets hurt,

338
00:29:43,920 --> 00:29:46,180
another steps in right away. No gaps left open.

339
00:29:49,750 --> 00:29:51,180
Zong Quan is a grandmaster.

340
00:29:51,510 --> 00:29:52,450
We're weaker,

341
00:29:53,360 --> 00:29:54,340
so we have to be extremely careful.

342
00:29:58,960 --> 00:30:00,420
We're outmatched. Lives are at stake.

343
00:30:01,070 --> 00:30:02,250
If you're worried, you can always...

344
00:30:02,270 --> 00:30:03,010
We live and die together.

345
00:30:07,550 --> 00:30:09,900
Less talk, more action. Let's practice!

346
00:30:12,550 --> 00:30:14,900
Again? I've bathed a hundred times already!

347
00:30:16,840 --> 00:30:18,880
♪Nightmares rage before the dawn♪

348
00:30:20,230 --> 00:30:22,050
Go wash again. Still too fragrant.

349
00:30:22,640 --> 00:30:27,880
♪Crushed ten thousand times, yet we embrace the pain♪

350
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:31,560
♪Heaven sent us here, no ordinary youths♪

351
00:30:32,080 --> 00:30:34,760
♪Through calamities, we do not hold back♪

352
00:30:35,360 --> 00:30:37,560
♪With righteous faith, we seal away♪

353
00:30:38,250 --> 00:30:41,000
♪The perils of the world♪

354
00:30:42,580 --> 00:30:44,140
♪All the way♪

355
00:30:44,580 --> 00:30:46,660
♪From the foot of the mountain to the peak♪

356
00:30:47,080 --> 00:30:49,380
♪I've passed through cliffs of blades and seas of fire♪

357
00:30:49,940 --> 00:30:52,500
♪Breaking the seal against thousands, returning in glory♪

358
00:30:53,380 --> 00:30:55,980
♪The ones who make it are the chosen ones♪

359
00:30:56,540 --> 00:30:58,740
♪With you, beneath the stars, the sun and moon♪

360
00:30:59,420 --> 00:31:01,980
♪This unquenchable fervor is a wonder to behold♪

361
00:31:02,650 --> 00:31:05,220
♪One final battle, we charge ahead♪

362
00:31:06,350 --> 00:31:08,980
♪The path of light is not far away♪

363
00:31:09,180 --> 00:31:10,230
♪All the way♪

364
00:31:10,670 --> 00:31:12,750
♪From the foot of the mountain to the peak♪

365
00:31:13,170 --> 00:31:15,560
♪I've passed through cliffs of blades and seas of fire♪

366
00:31:16,030 --> 00:31:18,880
♪Breaking the seal against thousands, returning in glory♪

367
00:31:19,470 --> 00:31:22,160
♪The ones who make it are the chosen ones♪

368
00:31:22,630 --> 00:31:24,920
♪With you, beneath the stars, the sun and moon♪

369
00:31:25,510 --> 00:31:27,470
♪This unquenchable fervor is a wonder to behold♪

370
00:31:27,470 --> 00:31:28,970
This formation requires everyone to be in sync

371
00:31:29,230 --> 00:31:31,490
and work together perfectly, or it's perilous.

372
00:31:32,440 --> 00:31:35,160
♪The path of light is not far away♪

373
00:31:52,550 --> 00:31:54,690
- Gelin! - Gelin! Are you okay?

374
00:31:54,960 --> 00:31:55,530
I'm fine.

375
00:31:56,160 --> 00:31:56,860
Mr. Hu.

376
00:31:58,750 --> 00:31:59,420
Mr. Hu.

377
00:32:01,270 --> 00:32:02,530
The monthly exam just ended.

378
00:32:03,070 --> 00:32:04,820
Think you're tough now?

379
00:32:05,640 --> 00:32:07,820
Practicing such a dangerous formation in secret.

380
00:32:08,750 --> 00:32:09,820
Do you have a death wish?

381
00:32:14,360 --> 00:32:16,530
We're plagued by crises inside and out.

382
00:32:16,920 --> 00:32:17,940
Without extra skills,

383
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:19,580
what if we get

384
00:32:19,600 --> 00:32:21,730
surprise exams?

385
00:32:21,750 --> 00:32:22,530
What then?

386
00:32:22,550 --> 00:32:23,490
Mr. Hu, am I right?

387
00:32:28,990 --> 00:32:30,010
Suit yourselves.

388
00:32:36,070 --> 00:32:36,620
Let me see.

389
00:32:43,160 --> 00:32:43,860
It's him.

390
00:32:52,790 --> 00:32:53,660
Lei Xiuyuan?

391
00:32:59,510 --> 00:33:00,690
Lifei sent you here, right?

392
00:33:01,360 --> 00:33:02,380
What tasty treats did you bring me?

393
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:04,450
Were you behind the spirit energy

394
00:33:05,310 --> 00:33:06,290
in the forbidden area?

395
00:33:09,550 --> 00:33:10,530
What spirit energy?

396
00:33:13,160 --> 00:33:15,490
Mr. Hu, I'll be blunt.

397
00:33:16,680 --> 00:33:18,290
You've been targeting me all this time.

398
00:33:19,600 --> 00:33:20,340
Why?

399
00:33:21,960 --> 00:33:24,380
Targeting you? Have I?

400
00:33:31,360 --> 00:33:33,210
Maybe a little.

401
00:33:36,230 --> 00:33:37,100
Want to know why?

402
00:33:44,510 --> 00:33:46,050
Because I hate you...

403
00:33:52,600 --> 00:33:53,940
for being better-looking than me.

404
00:33:59,470 --> 00:34:01,580
Mr. Hu, I'm just an ordinary person.

405
00:34:02,360 --> 00:34:03,490
I care nothing for sect traitors

406
00:34:04,230 --> 00:34:05,050
or reclaiming my kingdom.

407
00:34:05,920 --> 00:34:06,620
All I want in this life

408
00:34:07,360 --> 00:34:08,450
is to be ordinary.

409
00:34:09,510 --> 00:34:10,570
I joined the academy to protect myself.

410
00:34:11,510 --> 00:34:13,970
If you still suspect me,

411
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:15,700
you can just say it.

412
00:34:31,470 --> 00:34:31,940
By the way,

413
00:34:32,920 --> 00:34:34,050
Zong Quan is nearby.

414
00:34:34,880 --> 00:34:36,260
All of you stay put

415
00:34:36,280 --> 00:34:37,490
in the academy.

416
00:34:38,110 --> 00:34:39,130
Don't go looking for trouble.

417
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:56,380
Your Highness!

418
00:35:11,670 --> 00:35:12,900
We're getting more and more in sync.

419
00:35:16,990 --> 00:35:17,900
Lifei.

420
00:35:19,670 --> 00:35:22,300
You're getting more beautiful by the day.

421
00:35:23,150 --> 00:35:24,130
That's because you're

422
00:35:24,150 --> 00:35:25,340
starting to see me in a better light.

423
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:26,260
Really?

424
00:35:26,720 --> 00:35:28,820
I'm the kind of person everyone loves.

425
00:35:29,550 --> 00:35:30,610
Don't you think so, Your Highness?

426
00:36:09,630 --> 00:36:11,340
Smell this. Is there still a fragrance?

427
00:36:15,630 --> 00:36:16,260
Smell it.

428
00:36:42,840 --> 00:36:43,260
No.

429
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:47,090
Fine. But why are you running?

430
00:37:04,670 --> 00:37:05,260
Wait.

431
00:37:06,240 --> 00:37:07,780
The fragrance is clearly on Lifei.

432
00:37:11,070 --> 00:37:13,260
Strange spirit aura. It's her!

433
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:31,010
What secret is Lifei hiding?

434
00:37:32,400 --> 00:37:33,420
Why can't I help

435
00:37:33,440 --> 00:37:34,780
but be drawn to her?

436
00:37:36,320 --> 00:37:39,340
What does she have to do with my origins?

437
00:38:03,440 --> 00:38:05,530
Forget it. I'll focus on practicing the formation first.

438
00:38:09,590 --> 00:38:13,050
Once I master it and drive Zong Quan away,

439
00:38:15,070 --> 00:38:16,820
I'll get Hu Jiaping

440
00:38:16,990 --> 00:38:18,300
to tell me where my senior brother is.

441
00:38:25,550 --> 00:38:26,490
You're back again?

442
00:38:27,880 --> 00:38:28,170
You...

443
00:38:28,550 --> 00:38:29,650
I'll teach you a lesson.

444
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:55,740
Who goes there?

445
00:38:58,360 --> 00:38:58,900
Who?

446
00:38:59,470 --> 00:39:00,050
Who?

447
00:39:07,150 --> 00:39:09,010
My little chick can talk now.

448
00:39:10,280 --> 00:39:12,340
Cluck cluck.

449
00:39:12,550 --> 00:39:15,530
Cluck cluck.

450
00:39:39,550 --> 00:39:40,260
Cluck.

451
00:40:11,190 --> 00:40:11,900
What am I doing?

452
00:40:15,510 --> 00:40:18,300
No. I fell for that scumbag Zong Quan's trick again.

453
00:40:26,110 --> 00:40:28,050
Help!

454
00:40:38,150 --> 00:40:39,780
Your skills has actually improved?

455
00:40:40,590 --> 00:40:41,860
The academy is close by.

456
00:40:42,470 --> 00:40:43,700
Aren't you afraid the masters will come?

457
00:40:44,440 --> 00:40:44,940
Well,

458
00:40:45,240 --> 00:40:46,820
Mr. Zuo Qiu values me highly.

459
00:40:47,280 --> 00:40:49,700
Give it up. No one will find you.

460
00:40:49,960 --> 00:40:52,090
Tell me, where is the Divine Tree?

461
00:40:53,030 --> 00:40:56,130
Um, I can go back and ask around for you.

462
00:40:58,030 --> 00:40:58,780
Won't cooperate?

463
00:40:59,110 --> 00:41:00,700
Then come to Longming Sanctuary with me!

464
00:41:17,840 --> 00:41:18,380
Xiuyuan!

465
00:41:19,070 --> 00:41:20,010
Perfect timing.

466
00:41:20,470 --> 00:41:22,220
I'll take you back

467
00:41:22,720 --> 00:41:24,420
and find out where that traitor is hiding.

468
00:41:25,320 --> 00:41:25,780
Go now.

469
00:41:31,990 --> 00:41:35,260
Such feeble skills. You think you can stop me?

470
00:41:39,280 --> 00:41:40,420
I'll destroy your spirit meridians

471
00:41:40,840 --> 00:41:42,420
and dive into your sea of mind.

472
00:41:42,760 --> 00:41:44,780
Then I'll find the Divine Tree!

473
00:41:48,720 --> 00:41:50,820
Let... let her go.

474
00:42:05,590 --> 00:42:08,650
Cunning and sly. Might as well dig those eyes out!

475
00:42:24,920 --> 00:42:25,700
Spirit Slay!

476
00:42:38,200 --> 00:42:39,020
[The Eternal Fragrance]

477
00:42:39,020 --> 00:42:40,720
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

478
00:42:53,500 --> 00:42:57,020
♪The warmth within my arms♪

479
00:42:57,180 --> 00:43:00,700
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

480
00:43:00,820 --> 00:43:04,340
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

481
00:43:04,460 --> 00:43:07,940
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

482
00:43:07,940 --> 00:43:11,580
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

483
00:43:11,980 --> 00:43:15,260
♪I can no longer tell you♪

484
00:43:15,380 --> 00:43:18,900
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

485
00:43:18,940 --> 00:43:21,940
♪Utter that line♪

486
00:43:22,100 --> 00:43:24,140
♪Knowing love and hate♪

487
00:43:24,220 --> 00:43:28,620
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

488
00:43:29,340 --> 00:43:31,420
♪I still linger on♪

489
00:43:31,580 --> 00:43:35,860
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

490
00:43:36,020 --> 00:43:40,540
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

491
00:43:40,620 --> 00:43:44,140
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

492
00:43:44,220 --> 00:43:47,660
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

493
00:43:47,940 --> 00:43:51,180
♪I wish you well♪

494
00:43:51,340 --> 00:43:53,060
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

495
00:43:53,220 --> 00:43:57,900
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

496
00:43:58,500 --> 00:44:00,580
♪You're still screaming♪

497
00:44:00,740 --> 00:44:05,220
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

498
00:44:05,340 --> 00:44:09,820
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stand in its way♪

499
00:44:10,060 --> 00:44:13,020
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

500
00:44:13,140 --> 00:44:15,020
♪Leaping straight into♪

501
00:44:15,140 --> 00:44:19,900
♪That heartbreaking past♪

502
00:44:20,140 --> 00:44:23,660
♪Just to keep you safe♪

503
00:44:30,100 --> 00:44:33,420
♪My breath is about to stop♪

504
00:44:33,540 --> 00:44:37,060
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

505
00:44:37,180 --> 00:44:40,620
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

506
00:44:40,780 --> 00:44:43,980
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

507
00:44:44,100 --> 00:44:47,820
♪I smile as it ends♪

508
00:44:47,980 --> 00:44:51,620
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

509
00:44:51,820 --> 00:44:55,220
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

510
00:44:55,380 --> 00:44:58,500
♪To light your way through the night♪

511
00:44:58,580 --> 00:45:00,620
♪Knowing love and hate♪

512
00:45:00,700 --> 00:45:05,100
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

513
00:45:05,860 --> 00:45:07,900
♪I still linger on♪

514
00:45:08,060 --> 00:45:12,340
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

515
00:45:12,500 --> 00:45:17,020
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

516
00:45:17,100 --> 00:45:20,300
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

517
00:45:20,500 --> 00:45:22,460
♪With the light from my fingertips♪

518
00:45:22,540 --> 00:45:26,940
♪I build a paradise♪

519
00:45:27,100 --> 00:45:30,580
♪To wander with you♪
